juniSubscriberAgentV1.name: juniSubscriberAgentV1
juniSubscriberAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the Subscriber component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the Subscriber component was supported in JUNOSe 3.x system
        releases.
juniSubscriberAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for subscriber capabilities in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when local authentication support was added.

juniSubscriberAgentV2.name: juniSubscriberAgentV2
juniSubscriberAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the Subscriber component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the Subscriber component is supported in JUNOSe 4.0 and
        subsequent system releases.
juniSubscriberAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for subscriber capabilities in JUNOSe.
